                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.003/232: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Perkins</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-12-31T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 31, 1929—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>435. Your 1200, December 29, 2 p.m., and 1204, December 30, 5 p.m. For your
                    instruction and the guidance of American officials in China, the Department does
                    not regard the declaration of the Chinese Government as having altered the legal
                        <hi rend="italic">status quo</hi>. You may so inform your colleagues.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
